===Greeting===
'''Vaistinu vaskrse'''
#[[Happy Easter]] (''reply'')
#(''literally''): [[verily|Verily]] [[he]] [[is|was]] [[resurrect|resurrected]].
*:''Note:  This is only the '''reply''' part of the greeting.  It is the reply to [[Hristos vaskrse]].''
